ad any problems lately... so my only guess is they want some extra pocket money... 12 million dollars.. a year..<P>*edit*<P>Ahem..<P>We pay for several things:<P>1. The server and bandwith fees.<BR>2. Verant employees salaries.. very big ones too.<BR>3. We pay them to charge us for new content.<BR>4. Patches.. we pay for them to fix the game.<P><BR>Jesus.. the least they could do with all that money is allow me to move my character to another server that my friend is on.
